<br />\n但願人長久。可惜在兇猛的瘟疫和無情的政府政策面前，人命實太脆弱。武漢肺炎肆虐九個月，至今在港帶走百人生命，他們有的是夫妻，有的是臨終前也無法與家人告別的長者。雖然絕大部份逝者已逾古稀，但這些發生在不同家庭的悲劇，本應可以避免。<br />\n<br />\n疫潮首五個月，港人仍在適應。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6QbVmBSNIr7vL5-rUn-wG2PIaMU=/2279x1025/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UQWKIVBMVRE5DKCZ7QDAKBVE3A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6QbVmBSNIr7vL5-rUn-wG2PIaMU%3D%2F2279x1025%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUQWKIVBMVRE5DKCZ7QDAKBVE3A.gif&h=06ede604&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Q6IxOg4V024BSDKQwjPcc_H586A=/1199x1025/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5LYKVUSG6REBDGBBPYAXHCS6CE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQ6IxOg4V024BSDKQwjPcc_H586A%3D%2F1199x1025%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5LYKVUSG6REBDGBBPYAXHCS6CE.gif&h=b09d4743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冥頑不靈的林鄭月娥要等到七周後，才重新收緊豁免政策，但已一發不可收拾。死亡竟變成「例行公事」，一個個活生生的生命，記者會中的官員卻只能吐出一組組冷冰冰的編號。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"ec5ace82f869037794bfb43dcdf77a9e58fdfff7","tid":2200697,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T07:26:33.000Z","msg":"呢次第三階段疫情，就係林奠同老董為自己利益，比啲外國船員黎香港換班引起嘅，呢兩個犯人，要同香港人填命"},{"pid":"438a214d2fe46c59bacd3944006b470e7b6b8a60","tid":2200697,"uid":56550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T07:35:31.000Z","msg":"點解林鄭戴啊婆底褲都冇中肺炎"},{"pid":"4093faa2f9acfab2427a9948536eead0c99add96","tid":2200697,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T07:46:06.000Z","msg":"no.13 39歲係藍屍 抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係冇口德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}